{"tid":1295801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：77和平遊行無需衝擊已對政府做成重大威嚇，令習近平不知所措！","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T07:01:42.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3352d5cd91f93e55c632de46766b1bc489690c","tid":1295801,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/afu2nXxEqKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fafu2nXxEqKQ&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4VwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=beea7c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/afu2nXxEqKQ</a><br />\n77和平遊行令高鐵站停止運作，對政府造成好大威嚇，而今次並唔係騷擾死一個地方，影響短期，社會是可以接受，亦證明無需衝擊也能有效。和平遊行唔好行錯琪就能令對方冇得出手鎮壓， 不知如何是好。有跡象顯示估計有數萬人準備長期遊行，咁搞法隨時有成果。<br />\n<br />\n有小道消息指習種要十一前要解決好香港問題，抗爭者應為十一定下死線，否則大規模遊行！這樣做對北京立國70年的面子有嚴重威脅！<br />\n<br />\n對付佢要用柔性抗爭太極手法，政權出力時我們要縮，但要不停騷擾佢，咁佢就會撒少少，慢慢就越撒越多。若我們出強力隨時付出重大代價，咁喺唔得。"},{"pid":"80ecf9eba2e75ceb4d30d7bdf1d327be0db4e766","tid":1295801,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"收皮啦收皮啦.jpg"},{"pid":"197d07b38e7908ac0e70e1139cc31355efa86315","tid":1295801,"uid":39875,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUFPx2y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUFPx2y.gif&h=82053703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cd57239b418f439bafe0d4a20c919fc1ed699f7","tid":1295801,"uid":14132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"政府懶理，習近平定過抬油"},{"pid":"c9118060e7e0b1e215d4540d67091c584ce9b6f8","tid":1295801,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"出少句聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b30c9e5f010f716fda7033c945fbeb8a515b54","tid":1295801,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cd57239b418f439bafe0d4a20c919fc1ed699f7","tid":